{"id":"5c310e77b8f83c0017d0e0f5","title":"foreach文備忘録 - e-jigsaw.blogspot.com","image":null,"created":1234600080,"updated":1558880685,"lines":[{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f377f9","text":"foreach文備忘録 - e-jigsaw.blogspot.com","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f377fa","text":"[PHP]の制御文に foreach 文という構造があります。最初は軽視していた制御文だったのですが [http://www.blogger.com/e-jigsaw/#f1 *1] 、ちょっと前にかなり重要であることを認識させられました。最近は[Perl]とかでもあるようです。","created":1291134600,"updated":1558880646},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f377fb","text":"[*** 基本構造]","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f377fc","text":"code:_","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f377fd","text":"\tforeach(配列名 as 値用の変数) {","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f377fe","text":"","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f377ff","text":"基本はこんな感じです。配列名は普通に配列名、値用の変数というのはforeach文の中で使う値の変数のことで、Cでいうi [http://www.blogger.com/e-jigsaw/#f2 *2] になる変数です。PHPにもfor文はあります。Cを始め大半の言語で用いられている構文と同様です。","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37800","text":"code:_","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37801","text":"\tfor(初期値; 範囲; カウントアップ処理) {","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37802","text":"","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37803","text":"とまぁ、こんな感じです。なぜfor文ではダメなのでしょうか。","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37804","text":"[*** for文とforeach文の違い]","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37805","text":"例えば、配列に文字が入っていたとします。","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37806","text":"code:_","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37807","text":"\t$a = array(\"りんご\", \"まど\", \"ぺんぎん\");","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37808","text":"","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37809","text":"この配列の中身を全部表示したい時なんかには、for文では使い勝手がすごく悪いわけです。これが最たる理由 [http://www.blogger.com/e-jigsaw/#f3 *3] です。","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f3780a","text":"code:_","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f3780b","text":"\t$a = array(\"りんご\", \"まど\", \"ぺんぎん\");","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f3780c","text":"","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f3780d","text":"こんな感じにしてやると","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f3780e","text":"code:_","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f3780f","text":"\tりんご","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37810","text":"","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37811","text":"こんな風に表示してくれるわけですね。","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37812","text":"他に、","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37813","text":"code:_","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37814","text":"\tforeach(配列名 as キー変数 =","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37815","text":"","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37816","text":"という書き方もあって、これを使うと連想配列も簡単に表示できるようになるわけです。","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37817","text":"code:_","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37818","text":"\t$a = array(\"りんご\" =","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37819","text":"","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f3781a","text":"とすると","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f3781b","text":"code:_","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f3781c","text":"\t1:りんご","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f3781d","text":"","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f3781e","text":"と表示されるわけです。ちなみに、","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f3781f","text":"code:_","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37820","text":"\t$a = array(\"りんご\", \"まど\", \"ぺんぎん\");","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37821","text":"","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37822","text":"とすると、","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37823","text":"code:_","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37824","text":"\t0:りんご","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37825","text":"","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37826","text":"となります。ふと、備忘録をつけておこうと思ったので。最初はこの構文わけわかんなかったなー。","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37827","text":"[http://www.blogger.com/e-jigsaw/#fn1 *1] ：だってfor文あるじゃん！","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37828","text":"[http://www.blogger.com/e-jigsaw/#fn2 *2] ：iが一般的だよね？","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f37829","text":"[http://www.blogger.com/e-jigsaw/#fn3 *3] ：個人的には","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5ceaa19e4ade4d0000eb134b","text":"","created":1558880672,"updated":1558880672},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f3782a","text":"[* original: https://e-jigsaw.blogspot.com/2010/11/foreach.html]","created":1291134600,"updated":1291134600},{"id":"5c310e774ade4d0000f3782b","text":"#20100214 #0214","created":1291134600,"updated":1558880685},{"id":"5ceaa1a44ade4d0000eb134c","text":"","created":1558880678,"updated":1558880678}]}